title: Throwing A Surprise Party for a Show Member! + Bobby Performs The 'Tuesday Song' for 2/22/22!  Morgan’s Gives Her Review Watching Seinfeld Season 2 for the First Time
itunes:title: Throwing A Surprise Party for a Show Member! + Bobby Performs The 'Tuesday Song' for 2/22/22!  Morgan’s Gives Her Review Watching Seinfeld Season 2 for the First Time
description:
Bobby wants to celebrate a member of the show without them knowing. We try to guess who and what it could be before Bobby reveals. By request, Bobby per Morgan is watching Seinfeld for the first time and gave her review after watching season 2 on Netflix. We listen to another batch of BBS Theme Songs sent in by listeners to see who moves on to the finals.
